snippet: An article yesterday about the earthquake on Wednesday in California and a list of previous California quakes gave an incorrect date in some editions for one in the San Francisco Bay area in 1989. It occurred on Oct. 17, not Oct. 18....
lead_paragraph: An article yesterday about the earthquake on Wednesday in California and a list of previous California quakes gave an incorrect date in some editions for one in the San Francisco Bay area in 1989. It occurred on Oct. 17, not Oct. 18.
